# Anchored to repo root only — an unanchored "lib/" here previously matched
# frontend/src/lib/ too (and any future nested lib/ dir), silently
# excluding it from git tracking. No root-level Python build lib/ exists
# in this repo (venvs are separately covered by .venv/ / venv/ / env/
# below), so anchoring is safe and changes nothing for the actual intent.
/lib/
/lib64/
parts/
sdist/
var/
wheels/
*.egg-info/
.installed.cfg
*.egg
.venv/
venv/
env/

